Names Default To Here( 1 );
// ============================================================
// PROD TARGETING REPORT (v2 TEST)
// - Discrete target-regime filter (any target change boundary)
// - 3 chart columns per metric block:
//   1) Variability (PROD_MOP_PILOT)
//   2) Trend by PROD_MOP_PILOT
//   3) Trend by SITE_PROD_MOP_PILOT (toggleable)
// ============================================================

